    </nav>

    <div class="main-content">
        <h1>Ethical Potato Treatment Guidelines</h1>

        <div class="ethics-section">
            <h2>Proper Farming Practices</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Adequate spacing between plants (minimum 12 inches)</li>
                <li>Proper soil preparation with organic matter</li>
                <li>Gentle harvesting techniques</li>
                <li>Clean storage facilities</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ethics-section">
            <h2>Ethical Storage</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Cool, dark environments (45-50°F)</li>
                <li>Good ventilation</li>
                <li>No overcrowding</li>
                <li>Regular inspection for dignity</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ethics-section">
            <h2>Transport Guidelines</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Proper cushioning during transport</li>
                <li>Temperature-controlled vehicles</li>
                <li>Gentle handling during loading/unloading</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Contact: info@petp.org</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

