            <p>Documentation of potatoes stored in inhumane conditions without proper spacing or ventilation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="evidence-section">
            <h3>Exhibit B: Harsh Handling Practices</h3>
            <div class="blur-container">
                <img src="Pain2.png" alt="Rough potato handling" class="blurred" id="img2">
                <button onclick="toggleBlur('img2')">Show/Hide Image</button>
            </div>
            <p>Evidence of mechanical harvesting causing unnecessary trauma to potatoes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="evidence-section">
            <h3>Exhibit C: Negligent Transport Methods</h3>
            <div class="blur-container">
                <img src="Pain3.png" alt="Poor transport conditions" class="blurred" id="img3">
                <button onclick="toggleBlur('img3')">Show/Hide Image</button>
            </div>
            <p>Documentation of potatoes being transported without proper care or protection.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function toggleBlur(imgId) {
            const img = document.getElementById(imgId);
            img.classList.toggle('blurred');
        }
    </script>

